OL,3,CGovernment lines up insolvency firm in
OL,4,Ccase of Thames Water collapse
OL,6,FA spokeswoman for the Department for
OL,7,FEnvironment, Food & Rural Affairs
OL,8,F(Defra) said: "The Government will
OL,9,Falways act in the national interest on
OL,10,Fthese issues.
OL,12,F"The company remains financially
OL,13,Fstable, but we have stepped up our
OL,14,Fpreparations and stand ready for all
OL,15,Feventualities, including applying for
OL,16,Fa special administration regime if
OL,17,Fthat were to become necessary."
