OL,3,CGovernment lines up insolvency firm in
OL,4,Ccase of Thames Water collapse
OL,6,FThames Water, which has 16 million
OL,7,Fcustomers, remains locked in talks
OL,8,Fover a rescue funding deal with a
OL,9,Fnumber of senior creditors.
OL,11,FIn June, private equity firm KKR
OL,12,Fpulled out of plans to inject around
OL,13,F#4 billion of cash into the
OL,14,Ffinancially-stricken company in a bid
OL,15,Fto keep it afloat.
OL,17,FThames Water chairman Sir Adrian
OL,18,FMontague recently said the firm was
OL,19,Fstill in "crisis mode" as it seeks to
OL,20,Favoid special administration measures.
