OL,3,CGovernment lines up insolvency firm in
OL,4,Ccase of Thames Water collapse
OL,6,FA spokeswoman for Thames Water said:
OL,7,F"Our focus remains on a holistic and
OL,8,Ffundamental recapitalisation,
OL,9,Fdelivering a market-led solution which
OL,10,Fincludes targeting investment grade
OL,11,Fcredit ratings and returning the
OL,12,Fcompany to a stable financial
OL,13,Ffoundation.
OL,15,F"Constructive discussions with our
OL,16,Fmany stakeholder continue."
OL,18,FFTI Consulting has been contacted for
OL,19,Fcomment.
